short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Replaces Donald Trump with Angry Baby

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Replace every "Donald Trump" with "Angry Baby" Now every political web page you browse will have a bit of hilarity in it as you read, "President Angry Baby, throws another tantrum!" 

This is extensions puts Trump on the same level as Voldemort, he-who-must-not-be-named. By removing his name from the web, we hope to remove some of the hate he spreads and replace it with good-natured laughs.

Please help support us and our extension. Every dollar donated will go to the missmoosedevelopers children's college fund. There are four kids total and we hope that this extensions will help them as much as it helps you. You can donate directly at https://www.gofundme.com/president-angry-baby or send a Venmo to @missmoosedev

Thank you all so much!
